description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion part 3, which features more grilling! On Vanderpump Rules there is a shocking revelation at a tea party, and Hubbs enters the Winter House! After the recaps, Danny has a quick chat with Chris Baker, star/writer of The Estate, available now on VOD.


VPR/Winter House: 33:00ish

Chris Interview: 45:00ish
